#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:31
msgid ""
"Rotate the view around the point of interest. Click and drag :kbd:`MMB` on the viewport's "
"area. If you start in the middle of the area and move up and down or left and right, the "
"view is rotated around the middle of the area."
msgstr ""
"围绕着兴趣点旋转视图。在3D视图主区域范围内单击并拖动 :kbd:`MMB`。 如果从视图区域的中间开始"
"上下或左右移动, 那么视图就会绕着视图主区域中间旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:36
msgid ""
"To change the viewing angle in discrete steps, use :kbd:`Numpad8` and :kbd:`Numpad2` or :"
"kbd:`Shift-Alt-Wheel` (which correspond to vertical :kbd:`MMB` dragging, from any "
"viewpoint), or use :kbd:`Numpad4` and :kbd:`Numpad6` (or :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Wheel`) to rotate "
"the scene around the global Z axis from your current point of view. Finally :kbd:"
"`Numpad9` switches to the opposite side of the view."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 :kbd:`Numpad8` 和 :kbd:`Numpad2` 或 :kbd:`Shift-Alt-Wheel` (对应于垂直拖动 :kbd:"
"`MMB`)，或者使用 :kbd:`Numpad4` 和 :kbd:`Numpad6` (或 :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Wheel`)绕当前的视角全"
"局 Z 轴旋转场景，按离散步长调整视角。 最后，还可以使用 :kbd:`Numpad9` 切换到视图的另一侧。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:42
msgid ""
"Alternatively, if the *Emulate 3 button mouse* option is select in the *User Preferences* "
"you can press and hold :kbd:`Alt` while dragging :kbd:`LMB` in the viewport's area."
msgstr ""
"另外，如果在 *用户首选项* 勾选了 *模拟3键鼠标* 选项，在视图主区域范围内按住 :kbd:`Alt` 并"
"拖动 :kbd:`LMB` 模拟鼠标中键。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:45
msgid "Hotkeys"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:47
msgid ""
"Remember that most hotkeys affect the **active** area (the one that has focus), so check "
"that the mouse cursor is in the area you want to work in before you use the hotkeys."
msgstr ""
"请记住，大多数快捷键影响 **活动** 区域 (有焦点的区域), 所以在使用快捷键之前，请检查鼠标光"
"标是否位于要进行操作的区域."

