#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:66
msgid "Rotate the viewport camera around its local Z axis in 15° discrete steps."
msgstr "以15度的离散步长围绕其自身 Z 轴旋转摄像机视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:70
msgid "Panning"
msgstr "平移"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:76
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Navigation --> Pan`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`视图 --> 视图切换 --> 平移`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:77
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift-MMB`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad2`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad4`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad6`, :kbd:"
"`Ctrl-Numpad8`"
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift-MMB` , :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad2`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad4`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad6`, :kbd:"
"`Ctrl-Numpad8`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:80
msgid ""
"Moves the view up, down, left and right. To pan the view, hold down :kbd:`Shift` and "
"drag :kbd:`MMB` in the 3D View. For discrete steps, use the hotkeys :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad8`, :"
"kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad2`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad4` and :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad6` as with orbiting (note: "
"you can replace :kbd:`Ctrl` by :kbd:`Shift`)."
msgstr ""
"上、下、左、右移动视图。在3D视图中按住 :kbd:`Shift` 键拖动 :kbd:`MMB` 平移视图。 与旋转一"
"样，使用快捷键 :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad8`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad2`, :kbd:`Ctrl-Numpad4` and :kbd:"
"`Ctrl-Numpad6` 按照离散步长移动(注意: 你可以用 :kbd:`Shift` 代替 :kbd:`Ctrl`)。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:86
msgid ""
"For those without a middle mouse button, you can hold :kbd:`Shift-Alt` while dragging "
"with :kbd:`LMB`."
msgstr "对于那些没有鼠标中键的用户, 可以按住 :kbd:`Shift-Alt` 同时拖动 :kbd:`LMB`。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:91
msgid "Zooming"
msgstr "缩放"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:97
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Navigation --> Zoom`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`视图 --> 视图切换 --> 放大/缩小`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:98
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-MMB`, :kbd:`Wheel`, :kbd:`NumpadPlus`, :kbd:`NumpadMinus`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-MMB`, :kbd:`Wheel`, :kbd:`NumpadPlus`, :kbd:`NumpadMinus`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:100
msgid ""
"Moves the camera forwards and backwards. You can zoom in and out by holding down :kbd:"
"`Ctrl` and dragging :kbd:`MMB`. The hotkeys are :kbd:`NumpadPlus` and :kbd:`NumpadMinus`. "
"The :menuselection:`View --> Navigation` submenu holds these functions too as well. Refer "
"to the 3D View's *View* menu image above for more information. If you have a wheel mouse, "
"you can zoom by rotating the :kbd:`Wheel`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:107
msgid "If You Get Lost"
msgstr "如果你转晕了"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:109
msgid ""
"If you get lost in 3D space, which is not uncommon, two hotkeys will help you: :kbd:"
"`Home` changes the view so that you can see all objects :menuselection:`View --> View "
"All`, while :kbd:`NumpadPeriod` zooms the view to the currently selected objects when in "
"perspective mode :menuselection:`View --> View Selected`."
msgstr ""
"如果你在3D视图中转晕了，这并不少见。两个快捷键可以帮到你: :kbd:`Home` 更改视图以便您可以看"
"到场景中的所有对象 :menuselection:`视图 --> 查看全部`。另外当处于透视模式时， :kbd:"
"`NumpadPeriod` 缩放视图到当前选择对象  :menuselection:`视图 --> 查看所选`。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:118
msgid "Zoom Border"
msgstr "缩放区域"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:124
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Zoom Border`"
msgstr ":menuselection:`视图 --> 缩放区域`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:125
msgid ":kbd:`Shift-B`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift-B`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:127
msgid ""
"The *Zoom Border* tool allows you to specify a rectangular region and zoom in so that the "
"region fills the 3D View."
msgstr "*缩放区域* 工具用于指定一个矩形区域并放大，使该区域填充3D视图。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:130
msgid ""
"You can access this through the *View* menu, or the shortcut :kbd:`Shift-B`, then :kbd:"
"`LMB` click and drag a rectangle to zoom into."
msgstr ""
"可以通过 *视图* 菜单或者快捷键 :kbd:`Shift-B` 来访问，然后 :kbd:`LMB` 单击并拖动选择需要缩"
"放的矩形区域。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:133
msgid "Alternatively you can zoom out using the :kbd:`MMB`."
msgstr "或者，你可以使用 :kbd:`MMB` 拖拽出一个矩形，缩放框选区域。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:139
msgid "Dolly Zoom"
msgstr "滑动缩放"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:145
msgid ":kbd:`Shift-Ctrl-MMB`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift-Ctrl-MMB`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:147
msgid ""
"In most cases its sufficient to zoom the view to get a closer look at something, however, "
"you may notice that at a certain point you cannot zoom any closer."
msgstr ""
"在大多数情况下，它足以放大视图以便更近距离地观察某些东西, 然而, 你可能会注意到，到某一个点"
"之后，无法继续拉近距离."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:150
msgid ""
"This is because Blender stores a view-point that is used for orbiting and zooming. It "
"works well in many cases, but sometimes you want to move the view-point to a different "
"place. This is what Dolly supports, allowing you to transport the view from one place to "
"another."
msgstr ""
"这是因为Blender存储了一个用于旋转和缩放的视点。它在很多情况下都很好，但是有时要将视点移到"
"其他地方。这就是Dolly所支持的，将视图从一个位置移动到另一个位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/navigation.rst:154
msgid ""
"You can dolly back and forth by holding down :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl` and dragging :kbd:`MMB`."
msgstr "可以通过按住 :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl` 并拖动 :kbd:`MMB` 来回滑动。"

